              {
                "type": "input",
                "subType": "alert",
                "header": "Note",
                "content": {
                  "aws": "As part of the <a href='https://aws.amazon.com/free/' target='_blank'>AWS Free Tier</a>, you can get started with AWS Service Catalog for free. The AWS Service Catalog free tier includes creating applications, associating application resources, and managing application tags. For all other Service Catalog API actions, you get 1000 free API calls per account, region, and month. The calculations below exclude Free Tier discounts.",
                  "aws-cn": "As part of the <a href='https://www.amazonaws.cn/en/free/' target='_blank'>Amazon Free Tier</a>, you can get started with Amazon Service Catalog for free. The Amazon Service Catalog free tier includes creating applications, associating application resources, and managing application tags. For all other Service Catalog API actions, you get 1000 free API calls per account, region, and month. The calculations below exclude Free Tier discounts.",
                  "aws-us-gov": "As part of the <a href='https://aws.amazon.com/free/' target='_blank'>AWS Free Tier</a>, you can get started with AWS Service Catalog for free. The AWS Service Catalog free tier includes creating applications, associating application resources, and managing application tags. For all other Service Catalog API actions, you get 1000 free API calls per account, region, and month. The calculations below exclude Free Tier discounts."
